# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:41
translate spanish hwb_s12a_e1231a7b:

    # "My everything aches. It takes me a long, lazy minute to remember why I’m sitting up, forehead plastered to the steering wheel, rather than in my bed."
    "Todo me duele. Me toma un minuto largo y perezoso recordar por qué estoy sentada, con la frente pegada al volante, en lugar de estar en mi cama."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:43
translate spanish hwb_s12a_dc515481:

    # "I drove all through the night to get us to the Grand Canyon, arriving at the South Rim right around the time that I couldn’t keep my eyes open any longer."
    "Conduje toda la noche para llevarnos al Gran Cañón, llegando al Borde Sur justo cuando ya no podía mantener los ojos abiertos."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:45
translate spanish hwb_s12a_ecd025f4:

    # "We’re in a campsite, apparently, but I don’t remember anything past reaching the park’s edge and paying the entry fee. I probably shouldn’t have been driving, but we made it here alright."
    "Estamos en un campamento, aparentemente, pero no recuerdo nada después de llegar al borde del parque y pagar la tarifa de entrada. Probablemente no debería haber estado conduciendo, pero llegamos bien aquí."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:47
translate spanish hwb_s12a_73086a30:

    # "A sour taste pervades my mouth, courtesy of the empty energy drink at my side. I groan as I clamber up and head to go brush my teeth."
    "Un sabor agrio invade mi boca, cortesía de la bebida energética vacía a mi lado. Gimo mientras me levanto y voy a cepillarme los dientes."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:85
translate spanish hwb_s12a_a243bcd9:

    # "When I exit the bathroom, Marina’s waiting at the front, all dressed and ready to go."
    "Cuando salgo del baño, Marina está esperando al frente, toda vestida y lista para ir."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:89
translate spanish hwb_s12a_2a63431a:

    # Marina "Goooooood morning."
    Marina "Доброоооое утро!"

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:91
translate spanish hwb_s12a_d71b3704:

    # Amber "Morning."
    Amber "Доброе."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:93
translate spanish hwb_s12a_9b1e30aa:

    # "I’m still too sleepy to match her enthusiasm."
    "Aún estoy demasiado somnolienta para igualar su entusiasmo."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:95
translate spanish hwb_s12a_3e828652:

    # "Undeterred, she comes forward and presses a mug into my hands."
    "Sin inmutarse, se acerca y me pone una taza en las manos."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:97
translate spanish hwb_s12a_db231852:

    # Marina "I made you some coffee!"
    Marina "А я тебе кофе приготовила!"

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:102
translate spanish hwb_s12a_4cbb93b1:

    # Marina "But it was a couple hours ago, so it’s kind of cold now."
    Marina "Вот только уже пару часиков прошло, так что он немного остыл."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:107
translate spanish hwb_s12a_1131e1bc:

    # Amber "Thanks."
    Amber "И на этом спасибо."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:109
translate spanish hwb_s12a_36e5e143:

    # "It’s also brewed too weak, but I don’t tell her that."
    "También está demasiado aguado, pero no se lo digo."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:111
translate spanish hwb_s12a_227b1276:

    # "I drain my cup in seconds and then pour myself another. That’s also finished in a few long gulps."
    "Vacío mi taza en segundos y luego me sirvo otra. Esa también se acaba en unos cuantos tragos largos."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:115
translate spanish hwb_s12a_0ce70b12:

    # Marina "You really like coffee, huh?"
    Marina "Вижу, ты у нас любитель кофе?"

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:119
translate spanish hwb_s12a_c2a52d1d:

    # Amber "I guess. I think I’m just addicted."
    Amber "Типа того. Думаю, что это уже что-то вроде зависимости."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:121
translate spanish hwb_s12a_8e2bc97b:

    # Marina "You don’t even put any cream or sugar in it, right?"
    Marina "О, ты даже сахар или сливки не добавляешь?"

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:123
translate spanish hwb_s12a_fba5994a:

    # Amber "Nope. I always drink it black."
    Amber "Не-а. Предпочитаю крепкий черный кофе."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:125
translate spanish hwb_s12a_e526fadf:

    # "She wrinkles her nose in disgust."
    "Arruga la nariz con disgusto."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:129
translate spanish hwb_s12a_1ab9cedd:

    # Marina "I can’t stand the taste."
    Marina "Терпеть его не могу."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:133
translate spanish hwb_s12a_ce630044:

    # Amber "I noticed."
    Amber "Заметно."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:137
translate spanish hwb_s12a_f77a9598:

    # Amber "Have you gone and looked around yet?"
    Amber "Ты успела сходить на разведку?"

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:139
translate spanish hwb_s12a_0a4e1322:

    # "There are dozens if not hundreds of people milling around, and that’s just what I can see from here. Most likely treasure hunters."
    "Hay docenas, si no cientos, de personas deambulando, y eso es solo lo que puedo ver desde aquí. Probablemente cazadores de tesoros."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:141
translate spanish hwb_s12a_7f8f4d9e:

    # Marina "Look around? Without you?"
    Marina "На разведку? Без тебя?"

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:143
translate spanish hwb_s12a_bbc68457:

    # Amber "Yeah, it’s what, noon?"
    Amber "Ну да. А сейчас уже что, полдень?"

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:147
translate spanish hwb_s12a_373ad053:

    # Marina "Almost. But I didn’t wanna leave without you."
    Marina "Почти. Но мне не хотелось идти без тебя."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:151
translate spanish hwb_s12a_100f145f:

    # "That’s sweet of her."
    "Es dulce de su parte."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:155
translate spanish hwb_s12a_99e0a14b:

    # Marina "What if I got lost? You’re like my map."
    Marina "А что если бы я потерялась? Ты ведь у нас вместо навигатора."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:159
translate spanish hwb_s12a_c3bf8e82:

    # "Maybe not."
    "Quizás no."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:163
translate spanish hwb_s12a_f7294bfe:

    # Marina "Besides, it’s boring to go look around by myself."
    Marina "Да и к тому же, одной ходить скучно."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:167
translate spanish hwb_s12a_a8c3d1e6:

    # Amber "You think? I used to do it lots before we met up. Was nice to be alone and think."
    Amber "Думаешь? Мне, например, приходилось путешествовать одной до нашей встречи. Было приятно быть одной, в своих мыслях."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:173
translate spanish hwb_s12a_82ba0260:

    # "Her face falls. Seconds later, I realize my mistake and mentally kick myself."
    "Su rostro se desanima. Segundos después, me doy cuenta de mi error y me pateo mentalmente."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:177
translate spanish hwb_s12a_a96a03d4:

    # Amber "Not to say I don’t like having you around! I just meant it’s not so bad being on your own for a little bit."
    Amber "Нет, нет, я не имею в виду, что мне не нравится быть с тобой! Просто иногда бывает полезно остаться наедине с самой собой."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:179
translate spanish hwb_s12a_6be985f9:

    # "She ponders for a moment."
    "Reflexiona por un momento."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:183
translate spanish hwb_s12a_3572926d:

    # Marina "Well, I don’t like being alone."
    Marina "Ну, а я вот не люблю одиночество."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:189
translate spanish hwb_s12a_732e8c0e:

    # "A small frown makes me think she’s upset, but then it melts away and is replaced with her trademark smile."
    "Un pequeño ceño fruncido me hace pensar que está molesta, pero luego se desvanece y es reemplazado por su sonrisa característica."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:191
translate spanish hwb_s12a_39122d40:

    # "Something about how the sunlight frames her face right then makes my heart skip a beat. I want to admire her for longer, but I think my face gives it away."
    "Algo sobre cómo la luz del sol enmarca su rostro en ese momento hace que mi corazón dé un vuelco. Quiero admirarla por más tiempo, pero creo que mi cara me delata."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:193
translate spanish hwb_s12a_7061e905:

    # "Soon she shifts, asking with her eyes."
    "Pronto se mueve, preguntando con la mirada."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:197
translate spanish hwb_s12a_3a16d28e:

    # Marina "Something wrong?"
    Marina "Все в порядке?"

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:201
translate spanish hwb_s12a_7cb3475e:

    # "I shake my head to clear it."
    "Sacudo la cabeza para despejarla."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:203
translate spanish hwb_s12a_72bd88c6:

    # Amber "Nah, sorry. Just zoned out for a second. Lemme finish this coffee and then we can go."
    Amber "Ага, извини. Просто задумалась на секунду. Давай я допью кофе и начнем выдвигаться."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:207
translate spanish hwb_s12a_cf1563f7:

    # Marina "Okay!"
    Marina "Ладушки!"

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:211
translate spanish hwb_s12a_bad5c163:

    # Marina "I don’t know how you can be up and at ‘em just like that. Usually it takes me hours to wake up."
    Marina "Ума не приложу, как ты умудряешься так быстро вставать. Мне обычно требуется больше часа."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:215
translate spanish hwb_s12a_f426b4eb:

    # Amber "I know. I do a lot of waiting for you."
    Amber "Мне то не знать. Мне же вечно приходится тебя ждать."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:227
translate spanish hwb_s12a_de923862:

    # "Marina stomps over to play-hit me on the shoulder."
    "Marina se acerca pisando fuerte para darme un golpe de broma en el hombro."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:229
translate spanish hwb_s12a_d5ea40c3:

    # Marina "Meanie! I do my best for you!"
    Marina "Злюка! Я же стараюсь изо всех сил!"

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:233
translate spanish hwb_s12a_9c93cfeb:

    # Amber "Yeah, yeah."
    Amber "Да, да."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:237
translate spanish hwb_s12a_c39d5864:

    # Amber "There aren’t enough hours in the day for you to sleep as much you want."
    Amber "В сутках меньше часов чем тебе нужно для того чтобы выспаться."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:241
translate spanish hwb_s12a_e418ff7e:

    # Marina "What, are you saying I don’t need my beauty sleep?"
    Marina "Ну, мне ведь нужен здоровый сон, чтобы оставаться красивой, верно?"

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:245
translate spanish hwb_s12a_781def2a:

    # "She’s just kidding, but I freeze."
    "Solo bromea, pero me quedo paralizada."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:247
translate spanish hwb_s12a_db1a70f2:

    # "She is joking… right?"
    "Está bromeando… ¿verdad?"

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:251
translate spanish hwb_s12a_252ed066:

    # Marina "Amber?"
    Marina "Эмбер?"

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:253
translate spanish hwb_s12a_d4fa92ee:

    # "The jaunty tone in her voice is gone."
    "El tono alegre en su voz ha desaparecido."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:255
translate spanish hwb_s12a_defadd0a:

    # Amber "Yeah."
    Amber "Ага."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:257
translate spanish hwb_s12a_ed8e7095:

    # "I croak out a response."
    "Logro croar una respuesta."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:259
translate spanish hwb_s12a_27cd9594:

    # Marina "Zone out again?"
    Marina "Опять задумалась?"

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:263
translate spanish hwb_s12a_226084ea:

    # Amber "Something like that."
    Amber "Можно и так сказать."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:265
translate spanish hwb_s12a_50a574e0:

    # "Even I’m surprised by how off-guard that caught me."
    "Incluso yo me sorprendo de lo desprevenida que me tomó eso."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:267
translate spanish hwb_s12a_a0cb8a77:

    # "It was just a simple joke, but it was a little too relevant, seconds after thinking of how pretty she looked."
    "Fue solo una broma simple, pero fue un poco demasiado pertinente, segundos después de pensar en lo bonita que se veía."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:269
translate spanish hwb_s12a_ab26d972:

    # "Looks."
    "Miradas."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:271
translate spanish hwb_s12a_0c844430:

    # "I need to stop being so weird sometimes, or that’ll scare her off more than her finding out that I might, just maybe, could possibly have a crush on her."
    "Necesito dejar de ser tan rara a veces, o eso la espantará más de lo que ella descubra que tal vez, solo quizás, podría tener un crush con ella."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:273
translate spanish hwb_s12a_bbd6a434:

    # Marina "Maybe you just need more coffee."
    Marina "Может тебе нужен еще кофе?."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:275
translate spanish hwb_s12a_b00410e1:

    # Amber "Probably."
    Amber "Наверное."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:279
translate spanish hwb_s12a_86364cbe:

    # "Her grin gets huge."
    "Su sonrisa se vuelve enorme."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:281
translate spanish hwb_s12a_33aff836:

    # Marina "You need as much coffee as I do sleep!"
    Marina "Тебе на столько же нужен кофе, на сколько мне сон!"

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:283
translate spanish hwb_s12a_3a5fecec:

    # Marina "See! We’re even!"
    Marina "Видишь? Значит - ничья!"

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:287
translate spanish hwb_s12a_ed0be3e3:

    # "I laugh as I pour myself a third cup, tilting the pot to get the dregs."
    "Me río mientras me sirvo una tercera taza, inclinando la jarra para obtener los posos."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:289
translate spanish hwb_s12a_c8146e3b:

    # Amber "Maybe you’re right."
    Amber "Может ты и права."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:294
translate spanish hwb_s12a_ef4c606e:

    # "She prances back to the front door, nose held in the air like she’s won some great victory."
    "Ella brinca de vuelta a la puerta principal, con la nariz en alto como si hubiera ganado una gran victoria."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:296
translate spanish hwb_s12a_c7c5a9ea:

    # "I catch her peeking back to see if I’m watching, so I make a big show of rolling my eyes."
    "La atrapo echando un vistazo para ver si la estoy mirando, así que hago una gran escena de poner los ojos en blanco."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:298
translate spanish hwb_s12a_f7bf4b35:

    # "She sticks her tongue out in return."
    "Ella me saca la lengua en respuesta."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:300
translate spanish hwb_s12a_cfe9a3e4:

    # "When I set my cup down in the sink, Marina throws the door open and waits for me to step out."
    "Cuando dejo mi taza en el fregadero, Marina abre la puerta de golpe y espera a que salga."

# game/script/hwb_s12a.rpy:223
translate spanish hwb_s12a_f426b4eb:

    # Amber "I know. I do {i}a lot{/i} of waiting for you."
    Amber "Мне то не знать. Мне же вечно приходится тебя ждать."

translate spanish strings:

    # script/hwb_s12a.rpy:91
    old "Brushing Teeth"
    new "Brushing Teeth"

